data.title: AT&T Leverages Nokia Cloud Platform To Modernize IMS Voice Core
data.description: AT&T and Nokia expand partnership to enhance voice core network. Upgrade to cloud-native architecture for faster deployment and automation.

data.title: Tesla Cybertruck Headed For A Sales Crash In 2025? Analyst Sounds The Alarm, Predicts Elon Musk-led EV Giant Will Move Less Than A Third Of Street Estimates
data.description: Tesla researcher Troy Teslike expects the EV giant to sell just 21,000 Cybertrucks in 2025, lower than the sales in 2024.

data.title: Electronic Arts Set To Report Q3 Earnings Amid Analyst Downgrade, FC Franchise Concerns, 16% Year-To-Date Stock Decline
data.description: Electronic Arts reports Q3 earnings. Stock downgraded, faces scrutiny over growth potential and FC franchise.

data.title: PLTR Stock Surges Over 17% In Pre-Market After CEO Alex Karp Touts 'Untamed Organic Growth' In AI Demand
data.description: Palantir Technologies Inc. (NYSE: PLTR) shares surged by 17.3% in pre-market on Tuesday as the company's CEO, Alex Karp, emphasized a surge in demand for its artificial intelligence software, describing it as "untamed organic growth."

data.title: Bill Gates Says Nvidia's Jensen Huang 'Could Be Wrong' About Quantum Computing: QUBT, RGTI, IONQ React In Tuesday Premarket
data.description: Bill Gates said that it could take 3-5 years to develop logical quantum computing qubits while adding that the timeline could be longer.
